'''Jasper Calhoun''' is the son of [[Elliott Calhoun]].

==History==
While his father was fasting for his fourth aortic valve replacement, his mother's water broke and he was born prematurely. He was taken to the NICU, where he was said to be doing well. Before his father was taken to surgery, he asked to stop off to see Jasper.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He was born a month before his due date.
